title: 10 Top Tips for *Healthy* Productivity
author: Lavendaire
comment: Hi loves! Since a lot of you are asking, I’m posting the Plan w me for Sept tomorrow!!
The fact that u said " healthy productivity" makes me happy, because sometimes I see videos like "13h study with me"...

Yes I love that you called it “healthy” productivity. Because as we all know, in our western world it’s easy to fall into the trap of “hustle culture” and sacrifice our health and happiness for small gains.

Dear person that's reading this, we may not know each others but I wish you all the best in life!✨  Stop blaming yourself, accept things and go forward. Your smile is precious 🥰 all the keys of happiness is in your hands, so open it up 🔓
I can't even tell you how you are helping me so much to be the better version of myself 😭✨
description: Top productivity tips for a healthier, more balanced mindset. How to be productive without burnout, overworking, or obsessing about efficiency. Thanks Idenati for sponsoring this video! Be sure to check out Idenati at https://idenati.com/about?ref=Lavendaire
